  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdminUpdate
    Only admins may update loans directly on the site, but this table keeps track of those updates and makes them reversible just in case.
    CreationInfo
    Describes by which process a loan was created.
    Fullname
    Just a basic fullname that can be mapped to the database in order to prevent the bot from reusing the same one
    LendersCampContributor
    This describes contributors to the subreddit /r/lenderscamp.
    Loan
    Describes a loan in the database
    Recheck
    Describes a recheck
    Repayment
    Describes a repayment
    ResetPasswordRequest
    Describes a request to reset your password.
    Response
    Describes a response in the database
    ResponseHistory
    Responses are very flimsy; so we keep a good history on them.
    ShareCode
    Describes a share code
    User
    Describes a user
    Username
    Since it is not uncommon for people to create multiple accounts, and this is not strictly against the rules (unless the other account has broken some rule), it is appropriate to have a way of sharing history between multiple users.
    Warning
    Describes a warning that was issued to a user
